  channel: |md
    ### channel\<T\>
    **channel.hpp**
    ---
    Thread-safe MPSC channel
    ```cpp
    channel<request> requests_;

    // Send (producer)
    requests_.send({data});

    // Receive (consumer)
    auto msg = requests_.try_receive();

    // Check state
    requests_.empty()
    ```
  | {
    style: {
      fill: "#556B2F"
      stroke: "#6B8E23"
      stroke-width: 2
      font-color: "#E8DCC8"
    }
  }

  events: |md
    ### Event Primitives
    **event.hpp**
    ---
    ```cpp
    auto_reset_event
      // Signal once, auto-reset

    manual_reset_event
      // Signal stays set

    async_auto_event
      // Coroutine-awaitable event
      co_await event;
    ```
  | {
