  sync_vs_async: |md
    ### Sync vs Async Mutations
    ```cpp
    // During init (single-threaded)
    mutate_sync(g)
      // Uses add_gene_direct()
      // No channel overhead

    // During evolution (multi-threaded)
    co_await mutate(g)
      // Uses request_innovation_async()
      // Proper channel coordination
    ```
  | {
